'''Lukáš Červ''' (born 10 April 2001) is a [[Czech Republic|Czech]] professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[central midfielder]] for [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]] and the [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic national team]].

==Club career==
Červ played for the youth team of [[SK Slavia Prague]], with which he also played in the [[2019–20 UEFA Youth League]]. He made his senior league debut for Slavia Prague on 5 July 2020 in their [[Czech First League]] 3–1 away win against [[FC Slovan Liberec|Slovan Liberec]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Lukáš Červ|url=http://en.chanceliga.cz/hrac/3873-lukas-cerv|work=Chance Liga|access-date=2023-09-07}}</ref> He then spent the 2020–21 season on loan at [[FC Vysočina Jihlava|Vysočina Jihlava]] playing the [[Czech National Football League]], where he made 24 appearances and scored 7 goals. He spent the following season (2021–22) on loan in [[FK Pardubice|Pardubice]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Šestice hráčů míří na hostování|url=https://www.slavia.cz/article/18474-Sestice-hracu-miri-na-hostovani|publisher=SK Slavia Prague|language=cs|date=2021-06-22|access-date=2023-09-07}}</ref>

Before the 2022–23 season, he transferred to Slovan Liberec, where he became one of the busiest players.<ref>{{cite web |last=Havlen|first=Michael|title=Liberecký záložník Červ: Nečekal jsem, že budu nejvytíženější hráč|url=https://www.idnes.cz/fotbal/prvni-liga/lukas-cerv-fotbal-liberec.A230106_701289_fotbal_ald|publisher=iDNES|language=cs|date=2023-01-06|access-date=2023-09-07}}</ref>

On 5 January 2024, Červ signed a contract with [[FC Viktoria Plzeň|Viktoria Plzeň]] until 2027.<ref>{{Cite news |last=Malý|first=Jan|title=Staněk se těší na výzvu ve Slavii, chce pomoct k titulu. V Plzni jsou Valenta a Červ |url=https://www.sport.cz/clanek/fotbal-ceska-1-liga-stanek-se-tesi-na-vyzvu-ve-slavii-chce-pomoct-k-titulu-v-plzni-jsou-valenta-a-cerv-5019472|access-date=2024-01-05 |website=sport.cz|language=cs}}</ref>

==International career==
Červ played regularly for the Czech [[Czech Republic national under-18 football team|U18]], [[Czech Republic national under-19 football team|U19]] and [[Czech Republic national under-21 football team|U21]] youth teams.<ref name=facr>{{cite web |title=Lukáš Červ|url=https://www.fotbal.cz/repre/hrac/hraci/16333215|publisher=[[Football Association of the Czech Republic]]|language=cs|access-date=2023-09-07}}</ref> His 13 appearances for the U21 team includes two matches at the [[2023 UEFA European Under-21 Championship]], where he was part of the starting line-up in both.<ref>{{cite web |last=Preisler|first=Hynek|title=Po vyřazení z EURO jen tři dny ležel. Ještě to trochu bolí, říká liberecký Červ|url=https://www.sport.cz/clanek/fotbal-me-21-let-po-vyrazeni-z-euro-jen-tri-dny-lezel-jeste-to-trochu-boli-rika-liberecky-cerv-4313520|publisher=Sport.cz|language=cs|date=2023-07-03|access-date=2023-09-07}}</ref>

Červ received his first call-up to the [[Czech Republic national football team|senior national team]] ahead of the [[UEFA Euro 2024]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Nováček Lukáš Červ: Dokud trenéři nezavolali, nominaci jsem nečekal a nevěřil tomu|url=https://www.fotbal.cz/repre/novacek-lukas-cerv-dokud-treneri-nezavolali-nominaci-jsem-necekal-a-neveril-tomu/a20474|publisher=[[Football Association of the Czech Republic]]|language=cs|date=2024-06-03|access-date=2024-06-04}}</ref> He debuted on 7 June 2024 in a 7–1 [[Exhibition game#Association football|friendly]] victory against [[Malta national football team|Malta]] in [[Grödig]], Austria, coming as a substitute to [[Mojmír Chytil]] in the 79th minute.<ref>{{cite news |first=Ondřej|last=Schejbal|title=Češi si s chutí zastříleli. Dva góly proti Maltě zaznamenal Chytil|url=https://tn.nova.cz/sport/clanek/559170-cesi-si-s-maltou-s-chuti-zastrileli-dva-goly-zaznamenal-mojmir-chytil|publisher=[[TV Nova (Czech Republic)|TV Nova]]|language=cs|date=2024-06-07|access-date=2024-06-07}}</ref>

==Family==
Červ's cousins are Martin and [[David Douděra]], both professional football players.<ref>{{cite web |last=Preisler|first=Hynek|title=S bratrancem Douděrou se ve Slavii minul. Věřím, že šance ještě přijde, říká Červ. Napodobit chce Kuchtu|url=https://www.sport.cz/clanek/fotbal-ceska-1-liga-s-bratrancem-douderou-se-ve-slavii-minul-verim-ze-sance-jeste-prijde-rika-cerv-napodobit-chce-kuchtu-3452251|publisher=Sport.cz|language=cs|date=2022-06-24|access-date=2023-09-11}}</ref>

